  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a multicenter, prospective observational cohort study, in which patients with chronic
      airway diseases including chronic obstructive pulmonary disease(COPD), asthma, asthma-COPD
      overlap syndrome (ACOS) will be recruited.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
